All patient interactions generate structured clinical data flowing to the provider dashboard in real time:

- MAT dose confirmations (time, adherence streak, side effects)

- Craving levels (0–10, timestamps, frequency)

- Pain levels (0–10, correlation with cravings)

- COWS withdrawal scores (per-symptom breakdown)

- Mood ratings (emoji-based + voice sentiment NLP)

- Sleep quality and duration

- CBT/DTx session completion (module, duration, progress)

- Voice journal entries (AI sentiment analysis)

- Trigger identification (tagged categories)

- SDOH screening responses (housing, food, transport, social)

- Appointment attendance confirmations

- Narcan kit status (doses, expiration, family training)

- Urge mode activations (timestamp, resolution)

- Relapse reports (self-reported, confidential)

- Gamification engagement (XP, level, active days, family rewards)

- App engagement patterns (features used, session duration, active days/month)

- Drug screen dates, results, compliance rate, and overdue alerts

- Group therapy attendance: session type, facilitator, duration, frequency

- Post-discharge transition data: 2-day contact, med reconciliation, follow-up status

- Functional status: employment, daily living, social support (monthly)

- SBIRT screening scores and severity categorization (annual/transition)

- Naloxone dispensing records: doses, dates, family training status (G2216)

- Between-visit engagement time for CCM/PCM care plan documentation

